OL,5, Warrants have been granted to allow the
OL,6, forcible fitting of prepayment meters  
OL,7, for the first time in months following 
OL,8, a scandal over the practice.           
OL,10,FA district judge has given Scottish    
OL,11,FPower permission to enter homes to fit 
OL,12,Fmeters after bills were unpaid.        
OL,14,FBut nothing will happen until approval 
OL,15,Fhas been given by energy regulator     
OL,16,FOfgem. No supplier has yet satisfied   
OL,17,Fall the criteria required.             
OL,19,FFitting was halted after agents broke  
OL,20,Finto the homes of vulnerable people.   
